						<summary>

						<p>In the same place as above.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of 18 <hi rend="italic">(paṇam)</hi> for food-offerings to the god Tiruneḍuṅgaḷam-uḍaiya-nāyaṉar by a certain Edirālā Sāmantar, son of Vīrappa-nāyakka Sāmantar <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Aḻagappa Sāmantar of Vaḷambakuḍi.</p>						

